Examples

data("vertical_jump_data")

m1 <- cv_model(
  `Post-test` ~ `Pre-test` * Group * `Squat 1RM`,
  vertical_jump_data,
  control = model_control(
    cv_repeats = 10,
    cv_folds = 3,
    cv_strata = vertical_jump_data$Group
  )
)
